36
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:28,418
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37
00:02:28,419 --> 00:02:31,180
[GASPS]

38
00:02:31,185 --> 00:02:32,840
Quentin?

39
00:02:35,134 --> 00:02:42,141
<i>♪ ♪</i>

40
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:51,550
Where am I?

41
00:02:55,140 --> 00:02:56,730
