77
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,257
Meh.

78
00:04:39,258 --> 00:04:40,759
No!

79
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:43,261
[GASPING]

80
00:04:43,262 --> 00:04:44,720
Whoa.

81
00:04:44,726 --> 00:04:46,307
